              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                汪译：“尽管我们的宪法具有历史局限和道德瑕疵，但我们宪法的用语仍然用了一些语词，此后世代的人们为此争论不休，而且他们有时竟然超越了见解分歧达成对他们的政治忠诚的理解转向。<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>原文：<blockquote><q>For all its historical contingency and moral imperfection,our constitutional language has set the terms within which previous generations have disagreed with one another,and sometimes has allowed them to move beyond disagreement to a transformed understanding of their political commitments.</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







